<a href="/wiki/Russian_Orthodox_Church" title="Russian Orthodox Church">Russia</a> | <a href="/wiki/Serbian_Orthodox_Church" title="Serbian Orthodox Church">Serbia</a> | <a href="/wiki/Romanian_Orthodox_Church" title="Romanian Orthodox Church">Romania</a> | <a href="/wiki/Bulgarian_Orthodox_Church" title="Bulgarian Orthodox Church">Bulgaria</a> | <a href="/wiki/Georgian_Orthodox_and_Apostolic_Church" title="Georgian Orthodox and Apostolic Church">Georgia</a><br />
